    "DatasetsDatasets are a very important part of deep learning, as they are the foundation for training deep learning models.",
    "We focus on the selected datasets for the DL4RE studies and summarize the results into a bubble chart, as shown in Figure 3.",
    "The x-axis indicates the RE tasks that the studies focused on, and the y-axis shows the size of data entries used in training and testing the involved DL models.",
    "The size of the bubble indicates the number of publications.",
    "As shown in Figure 3, we can see that 61% of the selected publications have a dataset size of less than 6000, which may be due to the difficulty and cost of data collection."
